  <scopecontent audience="internal" id="aspace_49391ffc0022d1f97210c6edd1e71efc">
    <head>Content Description</head>
<p>The collection contains documentation from various sources (NGOs, government agencies, project brochures, publications, and reports) covering reconciliation efforts in Cambodia in the post-Khmer Rouge era gathered by Laura McGrew during her PhD research.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <prefercite audience="internal" id="aspace_f74ea30917cc13cd299ceeac88661101">
